Thread Lifecycle:

1. New
   - Transition: start() -> Runnable

2. Runnable
   - Transition: run() -> Running
   - Transition: stop() -> Dead

3. Running
   - Transition: sleep() -> Blocked
   - Transition: end of execution -> Dead
   - Transition: stop() -> Dead

4. Blocked
   - Transition: stop() -> Dead

5. Dead
